Witchcraft:Will Smith's ex girlfriend from Giyani is the cause of his over growing ears Will Smith has always been known for his acting skills and his good looks. The talk light skinned yummy man has for years been every woman's dream man. What made him unique has always been his adorable unusual big ears. He has apparently dated a girl from South Africa at a place called Giyane who cursed him the day he broke up with her. She told him that his ears will keep growing until they crawl. He laughed it off but now can't keep quiet anymore as he watches his ears grow on a daily basis. Will Smith is desperate for any help that can help reverse the curse. The woman's phone is always on voicemail when he calls her.